First of all ___DO NOT DO ANY ASSESMENTS!!___ why? cause map is earliest alpha, and i want to ask _you_, worth it further development. If it is, i will continue work on it(add details, stuff and maybe secret), if not, i will do another map.
It is still wip and very experimental map, gameplay reminds Russian roulette game. You'll understand why when you will play map!
Anyway, this map is still playable.
It has 64 slots, buyzones, big breakable wall to your pleasure(i could do it bigger but compilator start whine! DAMN IT!) and small surprise in the centre of the map, beware!
Surprise activates after 1 minute from match start, be fast!
